---
layout: layout.njk
title: "Travel Stories | Fine Art Travel Photography | Fabrizio Vinciguerra"
description: "Fine art travel photography by Fabrizio Vinciguerra, exploring Iceland, Cappadocia, Switzerland, Vienna and Amsterdam through light, atmosphere and visual storytelling."
ogImage: "https://www.fabriziovinciguerraph.com/assets/images/social/og-image.jpg"
ogImageAlt: "Fine art travel photography by Fabrizio Vinciguerra"
---

<section class="collection-hero">

  <img
    src="/assets/images/travel.jpg"
    alt="Fine art travel landscape photographed by Fabrizio Vinciguerra"
  >

  <div class="collection-hero-content">
    <p class="subtitle">Collection 04</p>

    <h1>Travel Stories</h1>

    <p>
      Fragments of distant places, quiet journeys and unexpected light.
    </p>

  </div>

</section>

<section class="fine-art-story travel-story">

  <div class="travel-quote reveal">
    <p>
      Every journey begins long before the photograph.
    </p>
  </div>

  {% for photo in travel %}

    {% if loop.index == 1 %}
      <p class="travel-location reveal">
        Cappadocia · Türkiye
      </p>
    {% endif %}

    {% if loop.index == 5 %}
      <div class="travel-quote reveal">
        <p>
          Some places ask to be explored.<br>
          Others ask you to stop.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="travel-location reveal">
        Switzerland
      </p>
    {% endif %}

    {% if loop.index == 9 %}
      <div class="travel-quote reveal">
        <p>
          Silence isn't empty.<br>
          It is full of everything we forget to hear.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="travel-location reveal">
        Iceland
      </p>
    {% endif %}

    {% if loop.index == 15 %}
      <div class="travel-quote reveal">
        <p>
          The strongest landscapes leave the quietest memories.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="travel-location reveal">
        Vienna · Austria
      </p>
    {% endif %}

    {% if loop.index == 18 %}
      <div class="travel-quote reveal">
        <p>
          Every city tells a story.<br>
          Some whisper instead of shouting.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="travel-location reveal">
        Amsterdam · Netherlands
      </p>
    {% endif %}

    <figure class="story-image travel-image {{ photo.class }} reveal">

      <img
        src="{{ photo.src }}"
        alt="{{ photo.alt }}"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
        class="lightbox-image"
        data-full="{{ photo.src }}"
        data-title=""
      >

    </figure>

  {% endfor %}

  <div class="travel-closing reveal">
    <p>
      The journey ends.<br>
      The memory remains.
    </p>
  </div>

</section>